{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioning"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"macOS virtual machines don’t have a cloud-init equivalent. Spooktacular","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provides provisioning modes to bridge this gap. Today, SSH provisioning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is fully working. Disk-inject is in progress, and two more modes (guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"agent and shared-folder watcher) are planned.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Choosing a Mode","anchor":"Choosing-a-Mode"},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Mode","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Status","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Works without setup?","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Network needed?","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Best for","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Working","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need SSH enabled"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Cloned VMs with SSH"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"In progress","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fresh IPSW installs, CI runners"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need agent installed"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OCI images (future)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need watcher"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No-disk-modify environments"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"SSH (Working)","anchor":"SSH-Working"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After boot, Spooktacular discovers the VM’s IP, connects via SSH,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and executes your script. You get real-time output streaming.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash","code":["spook start my-vm \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision ssh \\","    --ssh-user admin"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires:"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" Remote Login enabled in the guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(System Settings -> General -> Sharing -> Remote Login).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Disk Inject (In Progress)","anchor":"Disk-Inject-In-Progress"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Before the VM boots, Spooktacular mounts the guest’s data volume","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and writes a standard macOS LaunchDaemon that executes your script.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is the only mode that will work on a completely vanilla macOS","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"install. This mode is currently being implemented.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash","code":["spook create my-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Guest Agent (Planned)","anchor":"Guest-Agent-Planned"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Spooktacular guest agent will communicate over VirtIO socket — a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"direct host-guest channel that works without networking. This mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Shared Folder (Planned)","anchor":"Shared-Folder-Planned"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The script will be delivered via a VirtIO shared folder. A watcher","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"daemon in the guest will execute new scripts automatically. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mode is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"API Collection","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"role":"collectionGroup","title":"Provisioning Virtual Machines"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/CLIReference"],["doc:\/